cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.DC 

The paper deals with deep neural networks and their compression, which are topics that are commonly studied in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). However, given that the focus is on compressing deep neural networks, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG, followed by cs.CV and cs.AI.
